    <title>基于hexo搭建博客出现的问题</title>
    <link href="https://kyrie17.github.io/2019/01/26/%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8Ehexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <id>https://kyrie17.github.io/2019/01/26/基于hexo搭建博客出现的问题/</id>
    <published>2019-01-26T13:57:31.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-01-27T06:23:30.992Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>基于hexo搭建博客出现的问题</h1><p>[TOC]</p><h2>基于hexo框架搭建个人博客</h2><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26625249" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可以参考这篇知乎</a></p><h2>简单介绍一下站点中的结构</h2><p><img src="/img/blog.png" alt="blog"></p><p>经常用到的就是source、themes两个文件夹以及_config.yml文件</p><ul><li><p>source</p><p>此文件夹中包含的是你写的博客以及标签页、分类页、关于页等等</p></li><li><p>themes</p><p>此文件夹中放置的是你下载的主题</p><ul><li><img src="/img/blog1.png" alt="blog1"></li><li>在里面主题中又有比较常用的source文件夹和_config.yml文件<ul><li>source文件中存放的是css、js以及图片等文件</li><li>_config.yml中是主题的配置文件</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>_config.yml中是配置你站点的信息</p></li></ul><h2>搭建过程中出现的几个小问题</h2><h3>新建tags、categories、about页面</h3><p>在下载自己喜欢的主题后，是没有tags、categories、about这三个页面的，需要自己新建新建这三个页面的示例如下：</p><ol><li><p>使用：hexo new page &quot; &quot; 新建页面。<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;tags&quot;//新建tags标签页</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;categories&quot;  //新建categories分类页</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;about&quot;//新建about关于我页</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li><li><p>在主题的 _config.yml 文件中的 menu 中进行匹配不同主题 _config. yml文件有区别<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line"> home: /      //主页</span><br><span class="line"> categories: /categories //分类</span><br><span class="line"> archives: /archives   //归档</span><br><span class="line"> tags: /tags   //标签</span><br><span class="line"> about: /about   //关于</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"> 或</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"> menu:</span><br><span class="line">- page: home</span><br><span class="line">  directory: .      //主页</span><br><span class="line">  icon: fa-home</span><br><span class="line">- page: archive</span><br><span class="line">  directory: archives/    //归档</span><br><span class="line">  icon: fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">- page: about</span><br><span class="line">  directory: about/    //关于</span><br><span class="line">  icon: fa-user</span><br><span class="line">- page: rss</span><br><span class="line">  directory: atom.xml    //rss订阅</span><br><span class="line">  icon: fa-rss</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>这样这三个页面就新建好啦</p></li></ol><h3>为我们的文章添加标签和分类</h3><p>打开我们的文章按照如下示例添加：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: test</span><br><span class="line">categories://这就是文章的分类</span><br><span class="line">- tools</span><br><span class="line">tags:      //这就是文章的标签</span><br><span class="line">- hexo</span><br><span class="line">- markdown</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>这样就为我们的文章添加了标签和分类啦，如果在你的博客上还是没有出现标签或分类的话，请接着往下看。</p><h3>categories和tags页面不显示</h3><ul><li>方法一：</li></ul><ol><li><p>在scaffolds/draft.md中<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">----</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">tags: &#123;&#123; tags &#125;&#125;//添加此行</span><br><span class="line">----</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li><li><p>在scaffolds/post.md中<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">date: &#123;&#123; date &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">tags: &#123;&#123; tags &#125;&#125;//添加此行</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li><li><p>在tags/index中<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Tagcloud</span><br><span class="line">date: 2017-04-26 17:47:43</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">layout: &quot;tags&quot;     //添加此行</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li></ol><ul><li>方法二：</li></ul><ol><li><p>默认是没有 categories 和 tags 的需要<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;tags&quot; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;categories&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li><li><p>编辑 /tags/index.md /categories/index.md<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">layout: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">layout: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li></ol><h3>删除博客后再tags和categories中仍存在分类</h3><p>hexo删除无用的标签和分类啊，发过一次这个标签和分类就被记录下来了，更改这篇文章的分类和标签原有的分类和标签还是存在<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">待删除了所有的tags之后，在hexo deploy之前，先hexo clean一下。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3>在文章中插入图片</h3><p>使用本地路径：在hexo/source目录下新建一个img文件夹，将图片放入该文件夹下，插入图片时链接即为/img/图片名称。</p><h3>为你的Hexo加上评论系统-Valine</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/blue_zy/article/details/79071414" target="_blank" rel="noopener">原文</a></p><h4>简介</h4><p>Hexo的评论系统有很多，常见的有以下几个</p><ul><li><s>多说</s></li><li><s>网易云跟帖</s></li><li>畅言</li><li>来必力（liveRe）</li><li>Disqus</li><li>Hypercomments</li><li>valine</li></ul><p>首先多说和网易云已经倒下了，其次畅言需要备案，Disqus，Hypercomments和LiveRe都是国外的，加载速度贼慢，甚至有被墙的可能，寻觅了很久之后，从Material主题换成next主题之后，终于找到了一个好用的评论系统，那就是 Valine</p><p>我使用的是Next 5.1.3版本，本身就已经集成了valine，因此正常情况下是按照官方文档走就可以了，5分钟开启你的评论系统~</p><h4>开启Valine</h4><ol><li><p>注册Leancloud我们的评论系统其实是放在Leancloud上的，因此首先需要去注册一个账号<a href="https://leancloud.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">leancloud官网 点我注册</a></p></li><li><p>创建一个应用注册完以后需要创建一个应用，名字可以随便起，然后 进入应用-&gt;设置-&gt;应用key</p></li><li><p>拿到你的appid和appkey</p></li><li><p>填入appid 和 appkey拿到你的appid和appkey之后，打开主题配置文件 搜索 valine，填入appid 和 appkey如下：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">valine: enable: true</span><br><span class="line">appid: your app id </span><br><span class="line">appkey: your app key </span><br><span class="line">notify: false # mail notifier , https://github.com/xCss/Valine/wiki </span><br><span class="line">verify: false # Verification code </span><br><span class="line">placeholder: Go Go Go!</span><br><span class="line">guest_info: nick,mail,link </span><br><span class="line">pageSize: 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p></li><li><p>在Leancloud -&gt; 设置 -&gt; 安全中心 -&gt; Web 安全域名 把你的域名加进去</p></li></ol><p>刷新一下~ 是不是就能看到评论框了？</p><h4>tags、categories和about等页面关闭评论</h4><p>如下：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-01-12 14:08:00  </span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">comments: false//加入此行</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
